---
import MainLayout from "../../layout/MainLayout.astro";
import SectionContainer from "../../components/SectionContainer.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About me" description="I'm Jos Lee Villegas Pacheco">
  <SectionContainer>
    <div class="px-0 sm:px-20">
      <div class="mb-5">
        <span
          class="bg-green-400 py-1 px-4 rounded-xl text-green-900 border-2 border-green-800 font-bold text-sm"
          >Available to work</span
        >
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-5 mb-3">Who I am?</h3>

      <section
        class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center justify-center md:flex-row gap-x-20 gap-y-10 mt-10 mb-20"
      >
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold">
            Soy Jos, dise√±ador UX UI y Web based in Peru
          </p>
          <p class="">
            Since I was little I have been <strong class="text-amber-700"
              >passionate</strong
            > about the way in which web platforms or mobile applications without
            the need for a user manual, the way in which one can interact with them
            is simple and intuitive.
          </p>
          <p>
            During my school and university years my grades were good but the
            reason for them was that I thought about what would happen if the
            jobs that I was given, no matter how responsible I was, had
            something bad.
          </p>
          <p>
            This led me to have to <strong class="text-amber-700"
              >explore in depth possible errors</strong
            > that arise when carrying out each activity, which helped me to <strong
              class="text-amber-700">be detail-oriented</strong
            > with the responsibilities I have.
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          class="rounded-full size-40 sm:size-52 mt-10 sm:mt-0"
          src="perfilcv.webp"
          width="100%"
          height="100%"
          alt="Imagen de Jos Villegas"
          title="Imagen de Jos Villegas"
        />
      </section>

      <section
        class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center justify-center md:flex-row gap-x-20 gap-y-10 mt-10 mb-20"
      >
        <img
          class="rounded-full size-40 sm:size-52 mt-10 sm:mt-0"
          src="perfilcv.webp"
          alt="Imagen de Jos Villegas"
          title="Imagen de Jos Villegas"
        />
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
          <p class="">
            As a professional, I consider myself a <strong
              class="text-amber-700">perfectionist</strong
            >, which leads me to always <strong class="text-amber-700"
              >try to verify the smallest detail</strong
            > and explore other ways to get the job done.
          </p>
          <p>
            All this leads me to my design approach being guided by <strong
              class="text-amber-700"
              >the artistic attitude, scientific method, creative disorder and
              obsession with every smallest detail.</strong
            >
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not designing, I find myself exploring my creativity
            through music playing the guitar, books that talk about psychology
            or researching unknown things that catch my attention.
          </p>
          <div>
            <a
              download
              class="inline-flex justify-center items-center rounded-lg bg-[#4e4e4e] p-2 text-white border border-white hover:bg-[#272727]"
              href="CV_JosLeeVillegasPacheco.pdf"
              title="Donwload CV Jos"
              aria-label="Donwload CV Jos">Download CV</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Skillset</h3>
      <section
        class="flex flex-col items-start gap-x-60 sm:flex-row sm:items-center"
      >
        <ul class="list-disc ml-8 space-y-2">
          <li>UX Design</li>
          <li>UI Design</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-8 space-y-2 sm:mt-0 mt-2">
          <li>Wireframing</li>
          <li>Design Systems</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-3">Tools</h3>
      <section
        class="flex flex-col items-start gap-x-60 sm:flex-row sm:items-center"
      >
        <ul class="list-disc ml-8 space-y-2">
          <li>Figma</li>
          <li>Adobe XD</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-8 space-y-2 sm:mt-0 mt-2">
          <li>Miro</li>
          <li>HTML y CSS</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </SectionContainer>
</MainLayout>
